Package: BWSnooping
Title: Confidence invervals robust to bandwidth snooping
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Michal", "Kolesar",
    email = "kolesarmi@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides critical values for constructing confidence
    intervals that robust to bandwidth-snooping, that is, they are valid
    uniformly over a pre-specified bandwidth range.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.3.0)
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
